      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just more words to fix it. what if the shell is all that's left? what if there's no \"real me\" waiting on the other side of this? it just feels like i'm dragging around a corpse every day and everyone is just smiling at the costume. it's so exhausting to pretend to be a person when i dont feel like one.",
